{"id": "oao1665702862509", "title": "Example: Dynamically Change HTML Attributes in ProcScript", "breadcrumbs": ["Developing Web Applications", "Dynamic Server Pages", "Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages", "Example: Dynamically Change HTML Attributes in ProcScript"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oao1665702862509.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">Example: Dynamically Change HTML Attributes in ProcScript</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   Setting DSP Widget Properties \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   Setting DSP Widget Properties \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sjv1665702773431.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:  Entity and Occurrence Properties in Dynamic Server Pages  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:  Entity and Occurrence Properties in Dynamic Server Pages  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lqr1719489288111.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/oao1665702862509.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/oao1665702862509.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/oao1665702862509.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530506\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530506\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oao1665702862509.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oao1665702862509.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oao1665702862509.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"oao1665702862509\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Example: Dynamically Change HTML Attributes in ProcScript\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can use the AttributesOnly widget in dynamic server pages to manipulate HTML in ProcScript.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"oao1665702862509__context_w995ab1b5b1_w996ab1b5_w997ab1\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"oao1665702862509__topic_d20597e1_d20598e1_d20599e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oao1665702862509__p_d20600e1_d20601e1_d20602e1\">In this example, you create a simple dynamic server page that enables the user to press a button to completely change the look and feel of the resulting web page.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"oao1665702862509__li_d9911e1_d9912e1_d9913e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"oao1665702862509__p_d20603e1_d20604e1_d20605e1\">Create a simple DSP with a non-database entity and four fields.\n In the Define Structure worksheet, use the indicated templates to create the fields, and set the properties as specified:</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__1\">\n Template\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__2\">\n Field Name\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__3\">\n Initial Value\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__1\">\n AttributesOnly\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__2\">\n Attributes\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__3\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__1\">\n StaticText (secure)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__2\">\n MyData\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__3\">\n This is data to display\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__1\">\n CommandButton (secure)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__2\">\n SetFormat\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__3\">\n Set Format\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__1\">\n CommandButton (secure)\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__2\">\n ClearFormat\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oao1665702862509__table_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1__entry__3\">\n Clear Format\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"oao1665702862509__fig_d20606e1_d20607e1_d20608e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"oao1665702862509__fig_w998ab1b5b3b1b3b3b1b1_w999ab1b5b3b1b3b3b1_w1000ab1b5b3b1b3b3_w1001ab1b5b3b1b3_w1002ab1b5b3b1_w1003ab1b5b3_w1004ab1b5_w1005ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Fields created in the Define Structure worksheet\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/attribsstructure.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"oao1665702862509__li_d9914e1_d9915e1_d9916e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the Write Script worksheet, program the detail triggers of these buttons to change the field properties of the ATTRIBUTES field.\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail ; of SetFormat field\npublic web\n$fieldproperties(ATTRIBUTES)=\"HTML:CLASS=format1\"\nend; detail</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"oao1665702862509__pre_ymg_gcg_scc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail ; of ClearFormat field\npublic web\n$fieldproperties(ATTRIBUTES)=\"HTML:CLASS=format0\"\nend;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"oao1665702862509__li_d9917e1_d9918e1_d9919e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the Design Layout worksheet, create the HTML layout.\n </span>\n<ol class=\"ol substeps\" type=\"a\">\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"oao1665702862509__li_d9920e1_d9921e1_d9922e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"oao1665702862509__p_d20609e1_d20610e1_d20611e1\">Copy the ATTRIBUTES, SETFORMAT, and\n                     CLEARFORMAT fields into the layout. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Copy special &gt;As unformatted HTML</span></span>. </p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"oao1665702862509__fig_d20612e1_d20613e1_d20614e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"oao1665702862509__fig_w1006ab1b5b3b5b3b1b3b3b1b1_w1007ab1b5b3b5b3b1b3b3b1_w1008ab1b5b3b5b3b1b3b3_w1009ab1b5b3b5b3b1b3_w1010ab1b5b3b5b3b1_w1011ab1b5b3b5b3_w1012ab1b5b3b5_w1013ab1b5b3_w1014ab1b5_w1015ab1\">\n<img alt=\"HTML layout showing elements for copied fields\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/attribslayout1.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"oao1665702862509__li_d9923e1_d9924e1_d9925e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Copy the MYDATA field and copy it inside the &lt;span&gt; element bound to the ATTRIBUTES field.\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"oao1665702862509__fig_d20615e1_d20616e1_d20617e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"oao1665702862509__fig_w1016ab1b5b3b5b3b3b3b1b1b1_w1017ab1b5b3b5b3b3b3b1b1_w1018ab1b5b3b5b3b3b3b1_w1019ab1b5b3b5b3b3b3_w1020ab1b5b3b5b3b3_w1021ab1b5b3b5b3_w1022ab1b5b3b5_w1023ab1b5b3_w1024ab1b5_w1025ab1\">\n<img alt=\"MYDATA field copied to layout\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/attribssource.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li substep substepexpand\" id=\"oao1665702862509__li_d9926e1_d9927e1_d9928e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Optionally, add some <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;br/&gt;</code> elements to provide some line spacing.\n </span>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"oao1665702862509__li_d9929e1_d9930e1_d9931e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"oao1665702862509__p_d20618e1_d20619e1_d20620e1\">Define the style classes in a CSS style sheet\n               used by the DSP, or inline in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;head&gt;</code> element. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;style&gt;\n.format1 {\nfont-size: .85em;\ncolor:#294e56;\nmargin: 0 100px;\npadding: 10px;\nborder: 1px solid #73afb7;\nbackground-color: #fbef99;\n}\n.pagestyle {\ncolor:#104E8B;\n}\n.format0{\nborder-left: none;\nborder-right: none;\nfont-size: 1em;\nbackground-color:#FFFFFF;\n}\n &lt;/style&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"oao1665702862509__li_d9932e1_d9933e1_d9934e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"oao1665702862509__p_d20621e1_d20622e1_d20623e1\">Compile and test the DSP. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">At runtime, when the user clicks on the SetFormat button, all the fields inside\n                  the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;div&gt;</code>tags of the Attributes fields are reformatted\n                  according to the <code class=\"ph codeph\">format1</code>style.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"oao1665702862509__fig_d20624e1_d20625e1_d20626e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Formatting Cleared (CSS: format0)</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Default formatting\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/attribsruntime1.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"oao1665702862509__fig_d20630e1_d20631e1_d20632e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Formatting Set (CSS: format1)</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Formatting after Set Format is clicked\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/attribsruntime2.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://learn.rocketsoftware.com/course/view.php?id=65\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Learn More\" class=\"image\" id=\"oao1665702862509__image_pcb_tm4_vdc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Learn_More_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530506\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530506\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Example: Dynamically Change HTML Attributes in ProcScript Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Example: Dynamically Change HTML Attributes in ProcScript You can use the AttributesOnly widget in dynamic server pages to manipulate HTML in ProcScript. In this example, you create a simple dynamic server page that enables the user to press a button to completely change the look and feel of the resulting web page. Create a simple DSP with a non-database entity and four fields. In the Define Structure worksheet, use the indicated templates to create the fields, and set the properties as specified: Template Field Name Initial Value AttributesOnly Attributes StaticText (secure) MyData This is data to display CommandButton (secure) SetFormat Set Format CommandButton (secure) ClearFormat Clear Format In the Write Script worksheet, program the detail triggers of these buttons to change the field properties of the ATTRIBUTES field. trigger detail ; of SetFormat field public web $fieldproperties(ATTRIBUTES)=\"HTML:CLASS=format1\" end; detail Copy trigger detail ; of ClearFormat field public web $fieldproperties(ATTRIBUTES)=\"HTML:CLASS=format0\" end; Copy In the Design Layout worksheet, create the HTML layout. Copy the ATTRIBUTES, SETFORMAT, and CLEARFORMAT fields into the layout. For example, choose Copy special >As unformatted HTML . Copy the MYDATA field and copy it inside the <span> element bound to the ATTRIBUTES field. Optionally, add some <br/> elements to provide some line spacing. Define the style classes in a CSS style sheet used by the DSP, or inline in the <head> element. For example: <style> .format1 { font-size: .85em; color:#294e56; margin: 0 100px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #73afb7; background-color: #fbef99; } .pagestyle { color:#104E8B; } .format0{ border-left: none; border-right: none; font-size: 1em; background-color:#FFFFFF; } </style> Copy Compile and test the DSP. At runtime, when the user clicks on the SetFormat button, all the fields inside the <div> tags of the Attributes fields are reformatted according to the format1 style. Figure 1. Formatting Cleared (CSS: format0) Figure 2. Formatting Set (CSS: format1) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}